## ğŸ“Œ Why This Repository?

Most beginners learn protocols theoretically.  
This repository helps you **understand how protocols actually work at hardware level** by:

- Direct register manipulation
- Pin Connect Block configuration
- Real peripheral behavior
- Polling-based communication
- Industry-oriented code structure

